{"text_id":22153,"tokens":["We"," investigate"," the"," performance"," of"," split","-","valence"," Gaussian"," basis"," sets"," in"," conjunction"," with"," the"," heter","ole","vel"," approximation"," in"," restricted"," Hart","ree","-","Fo","ck"," (","R","HF",")"," and"," second","-","order"," M\u00f8","ller","-","P","les","set"," perturbation"," theory"," (","MP","2",")"," for"," peptide"," models","."," The"," development"," of"," efficient"," model"," chemist","ries"," for"," peptides"," is"," crucial"," for"," exploring"," their"," complex"," conformational"," landscapes"," and"," biological"," functions","."," In"," this"," study",","," we"," assess"," the"," accuracy"," of"," several"," split","-","valence"," basis"," sets",","," including"," ","6","-","3","1","G",","," ","6","-","3","1","G","*,"," and"," ","6","-","3","1","1","G","*,"," in"," combination"," with"," the"," heter","ole","vel"," approximation",","," which"," involves"," the"," use"," of"," a"," smaller"," basis"," set"," for"," the"," core"," orbitals","."," Our"," results"," show"," that"," the"," ","6","-","3","1","G","*"," basis"," set"," with"," the"," heter","ole","vel"," approximation"," yields"," a"," good"," balance"," between"," computational"," efficiency"," and"," accuracy"," for"," peptide"," models","."," We"," also"," find"," that"," the"," R","HF"," and"," MP","2"," methods"," provide"," similar"," descriptions"," of"," the"," peptide"," conform","ations",","," suggesting"," that"," the"," use"," of"," MP","2"," may"," not"," be"," necessary"," for"," these"," systems","."," Overall",","," our"," study"," provides"," a"," comprehensive"," evaluation"," of"," the"," performance"," of"," split","-","valence"," Gaussian"," basis"," sets"," and"," the"," heter","ole","vel"," approximation"," for"," peptide"," models",","," which"," can"," guide"," the"," development"," of"," efficient"," model"," chemist","ries"," for"," these"," important"," bio","molecules","."],"sub_source":"arx